com.serena.dmclient.objects
Interface ItemToItemRelationshipType

All Superinterfaces:
DimensionsObject
public interface ItemToItemRelationshipType
extends DimensionsObject

Represents a Dimensions item to item valid relationship, consisting of a RelationshipName, parent Type and child Type.

getInheritParentRelationships

boolean getInheritParentRelationships()
                                      throws DimensionsRuntimeException
Returns whether to inherit parent relationships when creating a new revision. If this flag is set to true, new revisions of the child item will inherit all the parent relationships associated with the base revision it is being created from.

Returns:
true/false

DimensionsRuntimeException - if connection error or internal error occurs
